Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.57,0:00:06.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:09.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}莫名其妙地就倒下了  嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:12.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}突然眼前一黑  腳一軟…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}輕度貧血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼辦  去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想休息一下就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}補習已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:28.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一天不去也沒什麼大的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天就休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:29.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:31.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人不去打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與往人一起去了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與往人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知了撞進了往人的早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與往人一起去了車站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與往人一起去了神社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不可以看人家的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你就不會寫點別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  我覺得寫得滿好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:04.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽好  說實話你沒有寫日記的天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:07.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以今後不要總寫做過的事  要寫想要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  那樣就不是日記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:11.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  是日記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我會實現你寫的所有的願望的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:18.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與往人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還沒和你一起到過沙灘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:27.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那裏挖沙子啦  撿漂亮的貝殼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說  你不是每天都能看到海麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:34.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:35.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪你去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:42.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.76,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子說想要去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.01,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我卻沒能帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:41.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴病倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  一整天了都沒好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正在房間裏休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你去看看她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:52.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓她看到我這幅醉樣  病情就變得更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}先不管她  看我買了壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}咱們來高興高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊…  你剛才的舉動極大地傷害了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:06.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你為什麼要收養觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你為什麼收養了觀鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼嘛  原來她對你講了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是收養  是別人硬塞給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然我說了不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正因如此  她才無法向你撒嬌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:26.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有點負責感好不好！  你可是她唯一的親人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子要和誰變得親近時就會發作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我和那孩子之間保持著一定的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因此才能生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}根本不像一對母女是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:41.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我自己也不是她真正的母親  所以什麼也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真難吃  買錯東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}女孩在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最初是個天空的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.20,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夢漸漸地追溯著過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:05.22,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是那個夢在侵蝕著女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.70,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}漸漸地  她會開始感覺到本不該有的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:12.35,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不久  女孩將會忘記一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:17.47,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}甚至連自己最親近的人都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.97,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後在做完最後一場夢的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.20,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}女孩會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.56,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子一直孤零零的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.96,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為兩個人的心靠近的話  兩個人都會病倒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.96,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}兩個人都無法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.34,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以那個女孩說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「離開我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是個善良並且堅強的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.96,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也正因此我才能活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.44,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是  那孩子卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在這片天空中  有一個擁有一雙翅膀的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:56.06,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她總是孤零零的一個人  長不大就消逝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.86,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人重複著那個悲傷的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去旅行！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對  一個人悠然地去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:08.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}溫泉之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底在想什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她…  觀鈴怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:18.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別太接近她的話  也就不會發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴正在做著一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是那個夢把觀鈴弄成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:26.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想起了媽媽說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:33.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我媽媽以前也遇到過這種病狀的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再過不久  觀鈴會忘記一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}忘記我  也忘記你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後在做完最後一場夢的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  可能會死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:48.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說  開玩笑也得分輕重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這不是玩笑  觀鈴她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:52.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:57.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我進來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼  醒著呢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  剛醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我聽到了媽媽的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  說是出去一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我非常喜歡媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}慢慢走  不用勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:32.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:44.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:49.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明明每天都走過這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海有這麼遙遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又要發作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一會兒就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海…  明天再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}平靜下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:32.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:35.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨晚我又做夢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這回是個快樂的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然是黑夜但天空很亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想那一定是節日祭奠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:49.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就那樣在遠處眺望著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人正在尋找的那個人和我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是相互聯繫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}誰知道呢  應該不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我思考了很多後得出一個結論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:07.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}願意聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的夢代表著另外的那個我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:15.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在  那個孩子正在痛苦著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要努力地做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為多做些夢  也許就會明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:26.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣  也許就能夠幫助那個孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:32.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人  我開始做這個夢並不是偶然的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我認為今年的夏天是不同尋常的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想努力去交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}於是便遇到了往人  然後開始做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這一切一定都是相互聯繫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我想努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想把這個夏天作為自己最美的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:53.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為這是和往人相遇的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:01.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我感覺舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:08.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？  這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}腳無法動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還是把聖叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要不去大的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:36.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  醫生肯定是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實往人也是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是我做的那個夢把我弄成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨天晚上我又做夢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一個旅途的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}旅途？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}尋找什麼東西的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在森林中走了好多天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然很累  但我努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為有喜歡的人陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:02.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喜歡的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我自己明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我每做一次夢  就會變得衰弱一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最終一定會像天空中的少女那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別說傻話！  怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  往人生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要去想什麼另外的那個你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}先把病養好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  觀鈴是堅強的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:49.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人！  往人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒事的話就不會那副表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我原本就是這副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  回床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不能不管往人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說了沒事了  不要太讓我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這痕跡是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:35.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒關係的  一會就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是我在你身邊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒關係  陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼大家只把我留下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:07.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼辦  還是叫聖來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}或是叫佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美風已經離開小鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要不叫個同學來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:20.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用了  我不想給別人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別說瞎話  你很想交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不喜歡一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有往人陪著我  其他的什麼都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}會不會給你添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:32.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想和往人一起去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在沙灘上玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}追逐跑啦  打水仗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最後大家揮手道別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過現在我先忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:52.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣到時候真去的時候會更高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:56.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我覺得差不多該離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再這樣下去的話  我倆都會病倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我決定逃離這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:15.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}離開這個小鎮  去一個再也不會見到你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:16.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:17.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:21.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們靠得太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就…  沒辦法了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒辦法了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:33.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就說嘛  一直一個人玩的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:34.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個暑假過的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和往人一起度過的這個暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:46.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已經沒車了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.90,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.38,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個…  今早的夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一個人被孤零零地關了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.05,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:07.42,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直在等著誰來帶我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:11.81,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我…我也想和往人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.31,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不能帶我一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:17.66,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不是想離開這個家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.03,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是必須要離開你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:24.11,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要我不在了  你的病應該可以治好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.00,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我是無法陪在你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:28.88,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.36,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.37,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  又說了傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.32,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那再見了…  保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.75,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.65,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.85,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  一個人也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.50,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是堅強的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:57.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人現在在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有沒有想著要讓看的人歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不這樣的話是無法操動人偶的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不能只想著要讓人偶動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:36.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要想著為什麼要讓人偶動起來  這樣人偶就會動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:50.24,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子說想去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:53.49,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我卻沒能帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:57.52,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人  這回你一定要救她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.18,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在這個人偶裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.06,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聚集著未能實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:08.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的母親  祖母等在身體衰弱前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.22,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都把自己的力量封印在了這個人偶裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.03,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了有一天有個人可以實現這個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.64,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我也會變成願望中的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如何使用這個人偶是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.89,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算忘記天空中那個女孩也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.29,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是往人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:33.52,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在某個小鎮上  你一定會和那個女孩相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.46,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果你無論如何都想救那個女孩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.01,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就心念這個人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我會和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}心念這個人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個大哥哥一直怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:58.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天熱中暑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:03.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拜託了  幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看這個  告訴我如何做才能變的有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:14.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如何做才能讓別人歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:19.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過沒什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別光是走  讓它再表演些其他的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比如裝成說話的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}表演段舞蹈如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}舞…舞蹈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要更用心些才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.21,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛才的表演非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}既有趣  又可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.04,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.29,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}謝謝啦  一直陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就加油吧  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.25,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哪裏都不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪在你身邊  讓你一直歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我找到竅門了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這回的表演一定很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以你要仔細看喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:47.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看啊！ 你笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼我一直都沒注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:05.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看著你的笑容就是我要追求的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就是我要追求的幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我哪裏都不會去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在我的身邊歡笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶…  觀鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:24.75,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你現在一定要想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.62,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自己必須做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:31.37,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我… 我想陪在觀鈴身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.84,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以的話  想從與她相遇的時候起重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.88,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這回一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.34,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}永遠陪在觀鈴身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本以為無法再起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:53.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你回來看我了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:02.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看  我又恢復健康了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我還可以加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶…  往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:24.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼──
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:28.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你為何在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有空說話的話趕快給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:34.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒見過你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:38.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正八位下左衛門大志 柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是從哪裏掉下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不知道我的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道  咱們才剛剛見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:48.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:50.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}竟然還有人不知道我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那可真是巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:57.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我奉命要保護的翼人的名字也是神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦～　真的是很巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:03.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是說嘛  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:46.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說到翼人  是神的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}當遇到饑荒和疫病時  祈禱神的力量來保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:53.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是可以直接和神對話的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:59.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所謂家族  就是大家聚在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:02.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想見媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:07.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有比見不到母親更殘酷的事了
