Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:23.42,AIR Title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}{\c&H0F0F0F&}{\shad0}{\bord0}千年前之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:09.92,AIR Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1366,1080)}{\fad(1000,0)}夏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:50.74,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}消失的航跡雲 我們目送遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:54.45,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}因眩目而逃開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:02:04.50,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}因懊悔而放手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:11.84,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}尚未抵達之地仍在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:18.80,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}只有將願望深藏心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:27.15,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}孩子們走在夏日的鐵軌上
